  14 Aug 2012; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Update metadata.xml so that it's the same as most other packages.

  01 May 2012; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> ruby-debug-0.10.3-r2.ebuild,
  ruby-debug-0.10.3-r6.ebuild, ruby-debug-0.10.4.ebuild:
  Drop ia64/sparc keywords

  25 Sep 2011; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  ruby-debug-0.10.4.ebuild:
  Simplify (and fix) dependency over ruby-debug-base since jruby support is
  gone.

  31 Jul 2011; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> ruby-debug-0.10.3-r2.ebuild,
  ruby-debug-0.10.3-r6.ebuild, ruby-debug-0.10.4.ebuild:
  Add ~ia64

*ruby-debug-0.10.4 (07 May 2011)

  07 May 2011; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +ruby-debug-0.10.4.ebuild:
  Version bump. This also fixes bug 366295. Drop jruby support since this now
  appears to be handled in a completely new way. See
  http://debug-commons.rubyforge.org/

  07 May 2011; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> -ruby-debug-0.10.3-r3.ebuild,
  -ruby-debug-0.10.3-r4.ebuild, -ruby-debug-0.10.3-r5.ebuild:
  Remove old versions.

  23 Jan 2011; Kacper Kowalik <xarthisius@gentoo.org>
  ruby-debug-0.10.3-r6.ebuild:
  Marked ~ppc64 wrt #322053

  25 Oct 2010; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> ruby-debug-0.10.3-r6.ebuild:
  Marked ~hppa (bug #337956).

